[{"Id": 1016640, "EnglishTitle": "PLEASE NOTE: Be it clear that the reason for presenting Translation is to understand Salaat and to recite in Arabic with concentration because reciting Salaat other than Arabic language (or Transliteration) is not correct.", "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": "Waazeh rahe keh tarjuma-e-namaz pesh karne ki asal wajah namaz samajh ke Arabi mein khuzoo aur tawajjoh ke saath namaz padhna hai. Kyu’n keh Arabi ya Roman-Arabi (Transliteration) ke siwa kisi aur zabaan mein namaz padhna sahih nahin hai.", "UrduTitle": "واضح رہے کہ ترجمۂ نماز پیش کرنے کی اصل غرض نماز سمجھ کے عربی میں خضوع اور توجہ کے ساتھ نماز پڑھنا ہے۔ کیوں کہ عربی کے سوا کسی اور زبان میں نماز پڑھنا صحیح نہیں ہے۔ اس لئے ہر ایک کے لئے نماز کی حد تک قرآن و عربی سیکھنا واجب ہے۔", "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1019085, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Saqar Ibn Dalf has narrated on the authority of Imam Hadi (a) (10th Imam) who said: “Whoever has any request to put before the Almighty Allah should take bath in Toos then should present himself before my hon’ble father Imam Reza (a) and perform Ziyarat of his shrine and perform 2 rakats namaz near his head and ask for his request in the state of Qunoot. If that request will not be related to severity of relationship or any sin, it will surely be accepted.” No doubt the shrine of Imam Reza (a) is one of the holy places of Heaven. Whoever will perform the Ziyarat at this place will be secured from the fire of Hell and will be awarded eternal place in Heaven.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Saqar ibne Dalf ne Imam Hadi (10th Imam) (a) se riwaayat ki hai keh unho ne farmaya: Jis kisi ko Allah (swt) se koi haajat ho, to usey chahiye keh woh Toos (Mashhad) mein ghusl kare aur mere jadd Imam Reza (a) ke rauze par ja kar unki ziyarat kare aur phir unke sar (feet) ki taraf ja kar 2 rakat namaz (fajr ki tarah) adaa kare keh jis ke qunoot mein apni jaaez haajat talab kare, inshallah zaroor qabool hogi. Be-shak jis jagah par Imam Reza (a) ka rauza hai woh Jannat ka ek hissa hai. Jo koi is jagah par ziyarat karega woh Jahannam ki aag se mehfooz rahega aur usey Jannat mein jagah ataa hogi.", "UrduDescription": "سقر ابن دلف نے امام ھادیؑ سے روایت کی ہے کہ انہوں نے فرمایا: جس کسی کو اللہ تعالی سے کوئی حاجت ہو، تو اسے چاہیے کہ وہ طوس میں غسل کرے اور میرے جد امام رضاؑ کے روضے پر جا کر انکی زیارت کرے اور پھر ان کے سرہانے کی طرف جا کر ۲ رکعت نماز ادا کرے کہ جس کے قنوت میں اپنی حاجت طلب کرے، انشاء اللہ ضرور قبول ہوگی۔ بےشک جس جگہ پر امام رضاؑ کا روضہ ہے وہ جنت کا ایک حصہ ہے۔ جو کوئی اس جگہ پر زیارت کرےگا وہ جہنم کی آگ سے محفوض رہےگا اور اسے جنت میں جگہ عطا ہوگی۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBl